description: Disturbances are derived using 3 fields related to geological stratification (eros1, eros2, eros3) and 7 fields related to the plant communities (v1pcm, v2pcm, v3pcm, ...). More than 3 disturbances are possible so we prioritise disturbances by ordering them in the mapTextNotNullIndex calls. BURN is given the highest priority. Any row with a valid disturbance value in one of the 10 source attributes is translated.

translation_rules: padConcat({inventory_id, src_filename, map_sheet_id, orig_stand_id, ogc_fid}, {4,15,10,10,7}, {'x','x','x','x','x'}, '-', TRUE, TRUE)
description: Concatenates five attributes to create CAS_ID

translation_rules: mapTextNotNullIndex(mod_1,13, 'BURN', mod_2, 13, 'BURN', mod_3, 13, 'BURN', mod_4, 13, 'BURN', mod_5, 13, 'BURN', mod_6, 13, 'BURN', mod_7, 13, 'BURN', mod_8, {'A','F','G', 'K', 'S', 'W', 'KA', 'FG', 'M', 'MG', 'MF'}, {'OTHER','OTHER','OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'SLIDE', 'SLIDE', 'SLIDE'}, mod_9,{'A','F','G', 'K', 'S', 'W', 'KA', 'FG', 'M', 'MG', 'MF'},{'OTHER','OTHER','OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'SLIDE', 'SLIDE', 'SLIDE'}, mod_10,{'A','F','G', 'K', 'S', 'W', 'KA', 'FG', 'M', 'MG', 'MF'},{'OTHER','OTHER','OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'SLIDE', 'SLIDE', 'SLIDE'}, 1)
description: Validation checks that at least one disturbance exists. Takes 10 source columns representing geological and forest dst codes. Returns the first not null result from the 10 sets of matchList combinations.

Validation checks that at least two disturbance exists. Takes 10 source columns representing geological and forest dst codes. Returns the second not null result from the 10 sets of matchList combinations.

Validation checks that at least three disturbance exists. Takes 10 source columns representing geological and forest dst codes. Returns the third not null result from the 10 sets of matchList combinations.
Because of its horizontal structure, the source data do not allow to associated at which layer the disturbance occurred.
